  <name>Brief</name>
  <summary>Browse command-line cheatsheets</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Brief is an app for browsing command-line cheatsheets. It lets you search through thousands
      of command-line tools across multiple platforms and languages, providing simplified help
      pages.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Works completely offline.</li>
      <li>Fuzzy search through the available commands.</li>
      <li>Filter platform specific commands (Linux, Windows, Android, etc.).</li>
      <li>View command help pages in multiple available languages.</li>
      <li>Change the command argument format between long (`ls --all`) or short (`ls -a`).</li>
      <li>Lets you update the cache within the app to download the latest data.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

